      "content": "it wasn't just \"a feeling\" though, it was like a literal data spike in my brain. i felt the tension build up right before the drop. normally people say it's just coincidence but when it happens this consistently it has to be more than that. like my nervous system is actually picking up on the patterns before they even hit the news. don't you think there could be some kind of biological connection to the way these massive data streams move?",
